messages.message:
Seeing sample files fail for paystub app in my browser window. Is anyone else seeing this or just me? Here is the link to the paystub app (https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/1d42e82b-a9bd-4039-93c3-9c1894651cca)

But it works when I try the same app in a new inprivate window.

I cleared cookies on my main browser window, but it still happens 100% of the time. Any ideas for what may be going on? @Eric Han
hmmm it seems to work for me now for some reason

you probably had a cached version of the frontend loaded in your browser, so clearing cookies in your browser won’t help

in the future, if you’re able to see the page successfully in another private window, go back to the window with the broken page and do a hard refresh (cmd + shift + r in chrome)
Yup, hard refresh worked for me :slightly_smiling_face:
